title: HQ Male Lumberjack Model - Warwick
description: A High Quality Rigged Model of a lumber jack ready for your use with both 2k and 512p textures to best fit the memory requirements of your game.
longDescription: A High Quality Rigged Model of a lumber jack ready for your use with both 2k and 512p textures to best fit the memory requirements of your game. The character is attached to an epic skeleton, so it's compatible with other market place animations. On the model's face there are 50+ Morphs Target of a smile, a blink, etc. allowing for full control over the face.
